How to use:

Copy the files in this folder into your new project and rename exampleCMakeLists.txt to CMakeLists.txt. Add your code to
subdirectories of your project folder, with one subdirectory per target (i.e., library or executable) and add each
target in the CMakeLists.txt. Then mkdir build, cd build, cmake .. and make to compile your project.